{"tid":2362876,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊:禁蒙面法判決重要 確認《緊急條例》符合《基本法》大型非法集會案件 須強調阻嚇和懲罰","createTime":"2021-01-11T18:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T02:22:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4176e8a0e78d1c08224db4707f0e43100a2a5dee","tid":2362876,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T18:40:29.000Z","msg":"律政司長鄭若驊昨在法律年度開啟禮致辭時，雖提到過去一年出現針對法官的無理肆意抨擊，指意圖向法官施加壓力只會「徒勞無功」，但未有提任何具體行動捍衞司法獨立，反不斷力撐港版國安法，反駁一國兩制受破壞之說是誤解，更力撐特首林鄭月娥委任國安指定法官安排。<br />\n<br />\n至於終院裁定民主派禁蒙面法司法覆核敗訴，鄭若驊亦有提及，指相關判決重要，確認《緊急條例》符合《基本法》，稱認同法庭觀點，而律政司據《刑事訴訟程序條例》提出的刑罰覆核申請大幅增加，鄭更特別提及，上訴庭在其中四宗案件中，重申黃之鋒案判刑原則，即在處理牽涉暴力的大型非法集會案件時，須強調阻嚇和懲罰作用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210112/ZZC2G7WDXNEOPB2Z4HF34FHZOA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210112%2FZZC2G7WDXNEOPB2Z4HF34FHZOA%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BerBpkLuHOqafswNxXmn3gI%3D&h=03cc976d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210112%2FZZC2G7WDXNEOPB2Z4HF34FHZOA%2F&h=8d17fe15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210112/ZZC2G7WDXNEOPB2Z4HF34FHZOA/</a>"},{"pid":"11d7257b580e924f4e0654f0c6ede6ed23ade6bd","tid":2362876,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T19:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34fc4095b305ec8ebc0d5d6ca5224d1110617e8d","tid":2362876,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T00:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i